[19:15] <rub_ixCube> :)

[19:15] <Zoffix> rub_ixCube: yeah, you can use when "x" | "y" to mean (when x or y)

[19:15] <Zoffix> huggable: Junction

[19:15] <huggable> Zoffix, Logical superposition of values: https://docs.perl6.org/type/Junction

